<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="related-adj">related <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'leɪtɪd/    美 /rɪ'leɪtɪd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>相关的；有关系的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>water-related diseases 
与水有关的疾病</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-related-to">(be) related to</h3>
<p>1.<strong>与…有关：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The “new four great inventions” are all related to China’s high-tech innovation.
“新四大发明”都与中国高科技创新有关。</p></div></div>